title: Ultimate HD Car Pack 2013 v1.3 - NON-ELS - Release #1
description:
Hi !

First of all, thank you for your support and your opinions on facebook page ! You guys helped a lot with this new version !

Again, it's here. New version of Ultimate HD Car Pack series. It's version 1.3 NON-ELS edition. Release #1. 
Whole new car list, better handling and much better cars. However, bikes and boats aren't edited because of the file size. 
Also finally finished license plates for all cars, not Liberty City anymore. 
I hope you'll fall in love with this new version like you did with v1.2.

* BASED ON 1.0.4.0 ! *
* BUT ALSO WORKS ON 1.0.7.0 * 


Also, there are new features with this car pack. Customized sounds for couple vehicles to make it more realistic. 
It sounds much better than stock sounds so I really recommend to use it, you won't loose any FPS with that. 
Another but not new feature is realistic car names. You may know it from previous version, but this time it's only for 1.0.4.0 patch version.


Here is the car list for you with name of the vehicle and year.
